{
  "stem": "9262.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And by this opportunity, I would mention that my uncle, who lived in a fashionable part of the town, at Gdansk 28, which was a very good neighborhood, had a lovely modern apartment house, where he occupied the whole second floor.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Germans-- German officers with the insignias of the German military government came up to his apartment-- two of them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of them said to him, we are requisitioning your apartment as our billet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you will have to vacate these premises within 48 hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, we two will be staying here now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you will have to make different arrangements for your sleeping arrangements.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And within 48 hours, you will have to leave it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My uncle who spoke well German, having done business with Germany and been many times over to Germany, because we were living in Germany, said to these two officers, yes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, it's no problem. 48 hours-- if you can give me 48 hours, we will leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he gave them his two front rooms, which was the bedroom in the front and the salon, what they called, like the dining room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were the two front rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He asked the-- the Polish maid that the beds should be arranged, because there were two officers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was, of course, a double bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had to get my cousin's little bed from the small room and put it into the big bedroom-- and other little alterations, which she done.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She served evening meal, because they came in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she served the evening meal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They asked the Germans what they would like to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They said, oh, we got our own food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't you worry, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You eat what you like.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
